Hinduism is one of the oldest religions in the world.It is a religion that is practiced in India and other parts of the world.
it has also been described by the modern term SanÄtana Dharma.
Hinduism features a vast pantheon of deities, including prominent figures like Ganesha, Lakshmi, Saraswati, Hanuman, Parvati, Durga, Kali, Krishna, and Rama. 
Holy Trinity of Hinduism
Lord Bramha-The Creator
Lord Vishnu-The Operator
Lord Shiva-The Destroyer
The major Hindu scriptures are the Vedas, the Upanishads, the Puranas, the Mahabharata, the Bhagavad Gita, the Ramayana.
